text:
Michelle Nogueras (born 5 December 1988) is a Puerto Rican female volleyball player. She was part of the Puerto Rico women's national volleyball team at the 2010 FIVB World Championship, 2010 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2011 Women's NORCECA Volleyball Championship, 2012 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2013 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2013 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup.
She played for Criollas de Caguas.
